<subSubSection pageId="231" pageNumber="836" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="231.[1447,2653,1437,2175]" pageId="231" pageNumber="836">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1449,1796,1949,1978]" pageId="231" pageNumber="836">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. There is almost nothing known about the Aceh Rat, especially becauseit is only known from two specimens collected at the type locality. It may be found in 
<taxonomicName authority="Leuser" authorityName="Leuser" box="[2298,2521,2023,2057]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Mallomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="231" pageNumber="836" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="gunung">Gunung Leuser</taxonomicName>
National Park. Additional research is needed tofully understand its natural history, taxonomy, and conservation threats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
